    "     \"text\": [\n",
    "      \"    INFO - 10:18:45: *** Start MDOScenario execution ***\\n\",\n",
    "      \"    INFO - 10:18:45: MDOScenario\\n\",\n",
    "      \"    INFO - 10:18:45:    Disciplines: ASK BiofuelUseGrowthConstraint BiomassAvailabilityConstraintTrajectory BlendCompletenessConstraint CO2Emissions CarbonBudgetConsumedShare CarbonOffset CarbonTax ClimateModel CumulativeCO2Emissions CumulativeCarbonOffset DetailedCo2Emissions DetailedCumulativeCO2Emissions DropInFuelConsumption DropInFuelDetailledConsumption DropinFuelConsumptionLiterPerPax100km ElectricConsumption ElectricityAvailabilityConstraintTrajectory ElectrofuelUseGrowthConstraint EmissionsPerRPK EmissionsPerRTK EnergyCarriersMassicShares EnergyCarriersMeanLHV EnergyCarriersMeans EnergyConsumption EnergyIntensity EnergyResourceConsumption EnergyResourceConsumption EnergyResourceConsumption EnergyResourceConsumption EnergyUseChoice FreightAircraftEfficiency FuelEffectCorrectionContrails GrossCarbonBudget H2OEmissionIndex HydrogenConsumption KayaFactors LCAFNoDegrowthConstraint LCAFUseGrowthConstraint LevelCarbonOffset LoadFactor NOxEmissionIndex NonCO2Emissions OperationsContrailsSimple OperationsInterpolation OptimizationObjectives OverallResourcesConsumption PassengerAircraftEfficiencySimpleASK PassengerAircraftEfficiencySimpleShares RPK RPKMeasures RPKReference RTK RTKReference ReducedMandate ResidualCarbonOffset SAFCO2NoDegrowthConstraint SAFFTGNoDegrowthConstraint SootEmissionIndex SulfurEmissionIndex TemperatureTarget TemperatureTargetConsumedShare TopDownCost TopDownCost TopDownCost TopDownCost TopDownEnvironmental TopDownEnvironmental TopDownEnvironmental TopDownEnvironmental TotalAircraftDistance YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator YAMLInterpolator\\n\",\n",
    "      \"    INFO - 10:18:45:    MDO formulation: MDF\\n\",\n",
    "      \"    INFO - 10:18:45: Optimization problem:\\n\",\n",
    "      \"    INFO - 10:18:45:    minimize cumulative_co2_2050(saf_co2_mandate_share_values_optim, saf_ftg_mandate_share_values_optim, lcaf_mandate_share_values_optim)\\n\",\n",
    "      \"    INFO - 10:18:45:    with respect to lcaf_mandate_share_values_optim, saf_co2_mandate_share_values_optim, saf_ftg_mandate_share_values_optim\\n\",\n",
    "      \"    INFO - 10:18:45:    under the inequality constraints\\n\",\n",
